1→import { Outlet } from '@tanstack/react-router'
     2→import { getCookie } from '@/lib/cookies'
     3→import { cn } from '@/lib/utils'
     4→import { LayoutProvider } from '@/context/layout-provider'
     5→import { SearchProvider } from '@/context/search-provider'
     6→import { SidebarInset, SidebarProvider } from '@/components/ui/sidebar'
     7→import { AppSidebar } from '@/components/layout/app-sidebar'
     8→import { SkipToMain } from '@/components/skip-to-main'
     9→
    10→type AuthenticatedLayoutProps = {
    11→  children?: React.ReactNode
    12→}
    13→
    14→export function AuthenticatedLayout({ children }: AuthenticatedLayoutProps) {
    15→  const defaultOpen = getCookie('sidebar_state') !== 'false'
    16→  return (
    17→    <SearchProvider>
    18→      <LayoutProvider>
    19→        <SidebarProvider defaultOpen={defaultOpen}>
    20→          <SkipToMain />
    21→          <AppSidebar />
    22→          <SidebarInset
    23→            className={cn(
    24→              // Set content container, so we can use container queries
    25→              '@container/content',
    26→
    27→              // If layout is fixed, set the height
    28→              // to 100svh to prevent overflow
    29→              'has-[[data-layout=fixed]]:h-svh',
    30→
    31→              // If layout is fixed and sidebar is inset,
    32→              // set the height to 100svh - spacing (total margins) to prevent overflow
    33→              'peer-data-[variant=inset]:has-[[data-layout=fixed]]:h-[calc(100svh-(var(--spacing)*4))]'
    34→            )}
    35→          >
    36→            {children ?? <Outlet />}
    37→          </SidebarInset>
    38→        </SidebarProvider>
    39→      </LayoutProvider>
    40→    </SearchProvider>
    41→  )
    42→}
